Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.92,0:06:11.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系 交给你了 希林
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.12,0:06:19.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,按Veda的预测 他的细胞异常已达到致死程度
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.31,0:06:24.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与Twin Drive有关?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.12,0:06:30.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道说…变革开始了?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.86,0:06:32.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刹那·F·清英
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.27,0:06:36.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙慈 找到她的机体了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.16,0:06:38.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到处都没有
