Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.56,0:06:40.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在找呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.64,0:06:46.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.43,0:06:46.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.87,0:06:52.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到还债的时候了 连同布林和迪万的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.19,0:06:57.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刹那 有两颗靠近母舰的陨石
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.84,0:06:58.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什…什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.09,0:07:01.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战斗中还东张西望
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.61,0:07:05.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么 去哪里了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.06,0:07:07.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)}滚开
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.46,0:07:08.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脑量子波
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.27,0:07:21.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找路易丝?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.82,0:07:23.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈哈哈哈哈哈
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.84,0:07:25.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这股加速粒子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.31,0:07:28.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我们的脑量子波兴奋不已
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.23,0:07:36.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错吧 阿勒路亚
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.51,0:07:42.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陨石里出现了MS
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.72,0:07:44.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会再吃他这招 拉塞
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.26,0:07:47.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白 导弹齐射
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.13,0:07:51.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.22,0:07:51.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.11,0:07:52.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,声音?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.89,0:07:53.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才那是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.87,0:07:55.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刹那…沙慈
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.37,0:07:59.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那光芒是? 又是幻听吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.33,0:08:01.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.03,0:08:06.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直在等 好想你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.52,0:08:12.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既非武器 也非破坏者
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.92,0:08:15.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和Gundam要改变
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.57,0:08:17.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路易丝
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.96,0:08:21.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.18,0:08:28.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路易丝 路易丝
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.96,0:08:30.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙…沙慈
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.87,0:08:34.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 是我 沙慈·库斯洛德
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.68,0:08:36.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙慈…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.75,0:08:46.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那光是?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.02,0:08:50.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,粒子释放量显示有通常的7倍
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.74,0:08:53.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是Twin Drive的…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.07,0:08:56.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,00之光
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.78,0:09:00.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刹那 我听到了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.84,0:09:05.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的声音 你的想法
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,====================================================
