Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.53,0:09:25.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路易丝
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.80,0:09:45.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好美
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.87,0:09:54.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五年前我们也像现在这样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.07,0:09:56.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起眺望着地球吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.70,0:10:01.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当时我看见这颗蓝色的星球
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.00,0:10:04.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下定决心在宇宙中工作
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.79,0:10:11.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望有一天能再和你一起看这片景色
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.05,0:10:13.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我当时是这么想的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.46,0:10:18.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明知不会再见了…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.16,0:10:27.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我们现在又相遇了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.39,0:10:29.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直在等你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.68,0:10:32.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这片宇宙中
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.94,0:10:41.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回来吧 路易丝 回到那段日子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.39,0:10:46.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回到那平和的日常生活
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.42,0:10:51.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.15,0:10:55.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么 你听到我的声音了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.29,0:10:56.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是天人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.22,0:10:58.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是被迫待在那里
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.99,0:11:00.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是指这些事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.99,0:11:01.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那又是?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.77,0:11:10.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我决心为实现统一世界的永久和平 献出此身
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.66,0:11:15.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为消灭祸乱世界的天人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.16,0:11:18.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是为妈妈和爸爸报仇
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.07,0:11:21.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路易丝…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.03,0:11:28.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别碍事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.25,0:11:32.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果从中作梗的话 我会杀你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.71,0:11:36.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很奇怪…不该这样
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.81,0:11:38.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你过去不是这种女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.10,0:11:42.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什么改变了你?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.29,0:11:48.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是自己的意志改变了我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.65,0:11:49.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是自欺欺人!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.44,0:11:53.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我了解路易丝
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.23,0:11:56.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道她是个温柔的女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.89,0:12:02.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道她为去宇宙刻苦学习
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.28,0:12:09.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道她故意任性 是为引起对方注意
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.71,0:12:16.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道她其实很容易寂寞
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.36,0:12:31.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.20,0:12:37.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路易丝
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.10,0:12:41.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙慈
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.24,0:12:43.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路易丝
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.72,0:12:47.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.55,0:12:52.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路易丝
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.93,0:12:56.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.99,0:13:07.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.02,0:13:08.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿勒威准尉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.54,0:13:12.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.41,0:13:13.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路易丝
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.43,0:13:13.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.15,0:13:16.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放开准尉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.12,0:13:23.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敢用奇怪的幻术迷惑准尉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.29,0:13:45.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那台机体 果然不善肉搏战
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.45,0:13:47.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的机体更差
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.91,0:13:49.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,净考虑优先火力
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.93,0:13:52.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可难说 TRANS-AM
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.35,0:14:11.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎…怎么会
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.67,0:14:19.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里逃
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.90,0:14:20.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Seraphim
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.28,0:14:29.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有话问你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.41,0:14:32.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如实回答 变革者
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.05,0:14:39.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,TRANS-AM到限制时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.73,0:14:41.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路易丝
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.36,0:14:44.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,休想带走准尉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.77,0:14:50.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到你了 安德烈少尉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.10,0:14:53.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这机体 增援吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.14,0:14:56.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么 为什么杀了上校?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.09,0:14:59.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比利斯中尉 为什么还活着
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.39,0:15:00.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回答我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.90,0:15:04.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也是叛徒吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.80,0:15:09.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有资格说吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.39,0:15:10.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛丽
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.09,0:15:15.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是增援
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.84,0:15:17.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,准尉 我们撤
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.13,0:15:26.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别追了 玛丽
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.90,0:15:27.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别拦我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.26,0:15:29.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要为上校报仇
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.94,0:15:31.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.48,0:15:36.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.02,0:15:40.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么都改变不了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.43,0:15:44.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,报仇也不会让人死而复生
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.27,0:15:47.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只会平添悲伤
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.77,0:15:53.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样做的话 所有人都会失去理智
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.59,0:16:00.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无处可去 驻足不前…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.84,0:16:10.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好一场闹剧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.77,0:16:12.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如此情意绵绵的战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.61,0:16:17.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拒绝当我的劲敌吗 少年
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.29,0:16:21.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然如此 就别怪我了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.82,0:16:36.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到这里就安全了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.94,0:16:39.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,席琳 我们今后…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.47,0:16:43.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前往事先和克劳斯定好的汇合地点
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.33,0:16:48.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去打探情况 你们在前面的小屋稍候片刻
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.29,0:16:50.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,席琳
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.72,0:16:54.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愿拿枪的你去了也是累赘
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.79,0:16:56.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,照顾好孩子们
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.34,0:17:04.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛莉娜 我和KATARON都还在战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.86,0:17:26.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙慈…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.36,0:17:32.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要去战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.72,0:17:40.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为找回路易丝 我有我的战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.59,0:17:54.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比利斯中尉在天人里
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.86,0:17:59.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲到底从什么时候开始背叛军队的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.46,0:18:07.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙慈… 沙慈…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.22,0:18:13.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,准尉 无法斩断这份思念吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.01,0:18:19.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么就由我 代你来完成想做的事 你的夙愿
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.54,0:18:27.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,半数以上的MS被击落 里维尔上尉沦为敌人俘虏?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.90,0:18:31.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名声远扬的特许员 也不过如此吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.82,0:18:34.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不明白我们的处事方式
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.02,0:18:36.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以就被俘虏?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.43,0:18:41.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次作战 由我们独自完成
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.31,0:18:44.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 这可了不得
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.68,0:18:47.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,期待你们的战果
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.14,0:18:49.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼 明白
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.56,0:18:57.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来晚了 这家伙就是变革者吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.79,0:18:59.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 毋庸置疑
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.26,0:19:01.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能否取下头盔?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.88,0:19:13.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初次见面 天人的各位
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.27,0:19:18.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我名叫里维夫·里维尔 是变革者
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.67,0:19:21.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能否和我们谈谈变革者的事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.67,0:19:24.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾纽
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.67,0:19:31.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉? 艾纽 偏离预定航线了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.43,0:19:33.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,修正下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.39,0:19:39.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾纽
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.86,0:19:40.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷特纳尔小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.34,0:19:42.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这是干什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.33,0:19:44.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.78,0:19:47.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这还用问
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.44,0:19:53.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是变革者
