Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.93,0:21:32.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,00 Gundam 只有我才配得上
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.12,0:21:35.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也这么认为吧 雷杰尼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.77,0:21:37.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然了 利冯兹
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.33,0:21:40.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼…口是心非
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.43,0:21:49.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,普特莱玛奥斯还没消息?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.21,0:21:51.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.61,0:21:52.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.66,0:21:56.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有把Veda的所在告诉天人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.36,0:22:00.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,变革者的计划必会被打乱
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.99,0:22:02.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而世界又会…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.20,0:22:04.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.38,0:22:06.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.49,0:22:09.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舰船操舵…控制不能
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.22,0:22:11.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对劲
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.86,0:22:12.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.97,0:22:15.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不清楚 系统被全部删除
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.31,0:22:17.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样下去的话
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.72,0:22:20.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道是来自Veda的介入
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.83,0:22:26.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你太调皮
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.15,0:22:31.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再敢自作主张的话…心里有数吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.72,0:22:36.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全无法控制
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.52,0:22:38.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脱出 准备小艇
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.97,0:22:41.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 舰船所有系统都没有反应
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.26,0:22:44.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妮娜?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.55,0:22:45.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妮娜·崔尼蒂
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.64,0:22:48.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听得见吗 这艘船上的系统失控
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.65,0:22:49.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帮帮我们
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.20,0:22:54.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傻瓜 这种事还用你说
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.47,0:22:56.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为那是我干的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.65,0:22:57.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你 你…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.09,0:22:58.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,显示屏上
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.95,0:23:01.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.87,0:23:08.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明什么都有 还贪得无厌
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.48,0:23:12.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己又外强中干
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.18,0:23:14.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我其实呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.75,0:23:19.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很早就看你不爽了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.60,0:23:23.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.20,0:23:25.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我去死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.99,0:23:36.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我要见证世界的…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.38,0:23:38.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,留美
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.28,0:23:40.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,变革…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.84,0:23:47.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太棒了 爽歪了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.44,0:24:04.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为变革者觉醒的艾纽 策划抢夺00
